# Planeta Mujer — Project Context

This repo contains Monica's portfolio AND the Planeta Mujer website (www.planeta-mujer.org). The `planeta-mujer/` directory is gitignored (deployed separately via FTP to Bluehost).

## Tech Stack

- Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS — no frameworks
- D3.js v7 for data visualizations
- GSAP for animations (older pages)
- Scrollama for scroll-driven narratives
- HTML Canvas for high-performance particle rendering
- TopoJSON/GeoJSON for geographic data
- Shared CSS: `planeta-mujer/shared/css/base.css` + `components.css`
- Shared nav: `planeta-mujer/shared/js/nav.js`

## D3 Course — Completed

Monica completed a full D3 course, building exercises along the way. She understands d3.scale, d3.transition, d3.shape, d3.hierarchy, and d3.force. When explaining code, connect new concepts to these foundations. Treat her as a learner who wants to understand WHY, not just copy-paste.

